      "span_text": "Cross-modal relations between performance movements and the sonic outcomes will also be inspired by the concept of Uncanny Valley, which was previously adopted in a composition that involved tension and relaxation structures in timbrally varied musical phrases generated by physical models [CITATION_1] ."
